{"tid":984099,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"名人齊為醫護打氣　譚校長：支持你　英雄輝：守住呀","createTime":"2019-01-16T13:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T13:55:46.000Z","uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b5fcdb7180e2eeb74031682e4aae6c25916a0d86","tid":984099,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T13:43:13.000Z","msg":"醫管局真係 on99，正經嘢唔做，攪埋呢D on9 嘢。<br />\n<br />\n年年流感, 年年都病床爆滿，都爆咗十幾廿年啦。<br />\n----<br />\n香港踏入冬季流感季節，公立醫院內科住院病牀日日爆棚，病人喺急症室輪候時間郁吓都幾個鐘頭，本來已經做到無時停嘅醫護同工作人員更加唔得閒，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">醫管局於是搵咗城中各界名人拍短片，為員工打氣。打頭陣嘅係殿堂級歌手譚詠麟同港足門將葉鴻輝，「譚校長」同「英雄輝」都齊齊話撐硬醫護</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局呢輯名為「全城集氣‧為醫護打打氣」的名人短片，今日下晝上載喺醫管局YouTube頻道。譚校長喺短片裏面，先哼唱幾句，然後就呼籲醫護人員同埋喺醫院做嘢啲哥哥姐姐，要「保護自己、注意健康，我哋支持你」；然後又話，而家係流感高峰期，請市民做好防範措施。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190116/s00001/62ae9269c9699494456ca05246b23f7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190116%2Fs00001%2F62ae9269c9699494456ca05246b23f7e.jpg&h=c9697ac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190116/s00001/1547642758384\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190116%2Fs00001%2F1547642758384&d=YSndJF%2BhQDO1%2B7GT4Ekm1pUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=d1eca161\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190116%2Fs00001%2F1547642758384&h=453552d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190116/s00001/1547642758384</a>"},{"pid":"0aa6662254bd25ecfa5c2c990d90c9d4b73387df","tid":984099,"uid":52062,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T13:45:14.000Z","msg":"打下氣解決到問題咩 學撚埋大陸d衰野 做實事啦屌"},{"pid":"96590421b8ad0970df58e99abb1f88205df4fdb9","tid":984099,"uid":96486,"like":6,"dislike":0